This is the source for the [Burocrazy][] website.

It uses [Jekyll][] to transform it into a static site that gets pushed to [Amazon S3][s3].

Installing on Mac
-----------------
Install [Xcode][] first.

    sudo gem update --system
    sudo gem install rake jekyll RedCloth
    sudo easy_install pygments
    brew install s3cmd

Installing on Ubuntu
--------------------

    sudo apt-get install ruby rubygems
    sudo gem install rubygems-update
    sudo gem install rake jekyll RedCloth
    sudo easy_install pygments

Running
-------

To build the website:

    rake

To run the built-in server:

    rake server

To deploy to S3:

    rake deploy

